{"tid":998994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港共政府喺資源分配上刻意製造零和局面，港人切忌中計，要團結反抗","createTime":"2019-01-28T11:31:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T02:59:20.000Z","uid":34884,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"82658c63bd43b6495d6e92bb0e556ebd25572eb2","tid":998994,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:31:29.000Z","msg":"港共政府最中意就係營造兩難局面<br />\n講到庫房同盈餘每一次只能夠集中分配畀某一階層同行業<br />\n<br />\n結果令唔同行業同階層既人爭個你死我活<br />\n撥錢畀A，B就出嚟嘈話A行業唔值得拎<br />\n撥錢畀B，A就出嚟講一大堆理論講點解政府唔應該畀錢B<br />\n<br />\n政府就用晒兩邊唔應該畀錢既理由<br />\n最後兩邊一個仙都唔畀<br />\n港共政府呢二十年期間都屢試不爽<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以再中計<br />\n每一個階層同行業既人出嚟發聲爭取<br />\n我地都應該無條件支持<br />\n咁樣先可以得到我地每個人想要既野"},{"pid":"dd060634426a717661cf27df53e7e9c63887ff17","tid":998994,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5bbf76c527727a1bd9bedbec4268b199346a4f74","tid":998994,"uid":34884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:47:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2956344707aa934b4b56a8fa71101e4834f66ce6","tid":998994,"uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:50:50.000Z","msg":"今次咁撚有point<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16770859ac53e8413837c28993d606983e338294","tid":998994,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T12:55:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd57e9eba5ee675bf716c73b2c5790faa110282","tid":998994,"uid":111571,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:05:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04df235d012e11f67168d2ab452d9229d0362b89","tid":998994,"uid":34884,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5fd57e9eba5ee675bf716c73b2